      "comment": "ZIPPING MIGALOO (2) produced a modest effort most recently when eighth at Horsham over 410m behind Pyrenees Ace (24.39) in a Grade 4/5. Was in the money prior to that. The form out of his last race has been franked. Better than last start and worth following up. BLUE TO BURN (4) was below best last time when fifth at this track but prior to that among the placings in quick time (23.22) at this track. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. CADILLAC BELLE (1) turned in a plain effort last time when sixth at this track over 305m behind Compton To Avoid (18.16) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Warrants plenty of respect. CADILLAC MAGIC (6) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
